{"tid":790784,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"你會點評 竊聽風雲 1 2 3","createTime":"2018-08-23T09:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T04:33:03.000Z","uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7143ff82ba0285d357c4fda69b42302cd5317454","tid":790784,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"3正，題材宏觀，人物多但係性格立體，每個人都用得好盡<br />\n四兄弟唔洗講，吳孟達客串個四大地產商代表真係狗公到有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯一唔好既係明明葉璇又正又做得好，又孝順又仆街又收兵又拜金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係個封面無佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2都正，吳彥祖做聰明絕頂孝順仔真係無得彈，成個劇本寫到好撚浪漫，最後三母子睇戲果幕真係眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n撚到古天樂 劉青雲狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過同3有同一個問題，係同竊聽個主題無乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1就角色唔特別，不過劇本好，好簡單就帶出個主題同故事。唔好就在於個結局好撚sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，個個都冚家剷<br />\n<br />\n有一幕都好深刻，係方中信做劉青雲個燥底綠帽上司，劉青雲笑住咁同方中信講左句 無所謂啦，之後方中信黑曬口面同劉青雲講 笑笑笑，有咩好笑呀笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d戲正到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會321咁排"},{"pid":"ca84a9224bb004cc932970b4d021cb3015249ac2","tid":790784,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/175649_130678712cdaeab074f1579bca902894.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F175649_130678712cdaeab074f1579bca902894.png&h=5bc1e154&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/175650_54032322b95d2a3b2f4d4af5c1bcc1e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F175650_54032322b95d2a3b2f4d4af5c1bcc1e6.png&h=b75ee235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c820b6a118ae0939ff3a6ae951bfd2370e5e3e75","tid":790784,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/175757_296068ca78ff9ae981d79cd9648df966.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F175757_296068ca78ff9ae981d79cd9648df966.png&h=af023a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾撚仆街個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522817e5a98882a622fe37dcc7cc088dd8ae60da","tid":790784,"uid":159577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:58:58.000Z","msg":"第二集最正，第3集有d眼高手低"},{"pid":"21680cf826c344ca2aa599b251ae3e7b72770864","tid":790784,"uid":84633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"第三集有野心<br />\n<br />\n題材捉得好<br />\n<br />\n係結局暴走"},{"pid":"2f7c0acf1caa2494994467ba48d40787a48d4a9b","tid":790784,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"3個故事唔得，2就最緊湊但個結局唔得，步步計算到最後都係靠曾冮失控先入到罪，1故事最好，每個人都有自己嘅陰暗面"},{"pid":"cc6db97d2c73446fa4e